description: Making Maryland proud with their savory goodness, Bentwood Smokers BBQ and Catering is bringing out some marvelously mouthwatering comfort cuisine. Their brisket is perfectly juicy, their pulled pork is unforgettably delicious, and their BBQ chicken is beyond finger-lickin’ good. Their sides of smoked Mac & Cheese, Baked Beans, Scalloped Potatoes, and so much more will all keep you coming back time and again to satisfy your cravings for this sensational food.And if you’re planning a big party, be sure to feed your guests only the best and call on Bentwood Smokers BBQ & Catering to come to you.
name: Bentwood Smokers BBQ and Catering
